data.description: Absolute paradise! This beautifully maintained home offers so much more than expected! This 1 acre lot is zoned OR and is complete with storage units (3), horse stables, carport, covered rear patio, and partially fenced yard. The home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths with an open floor plan and gas fireplace in the living room. Walk in closets and ceiling fans in every room! Plantation shutters are a fantastic addition and go throughout the entire home! Kitchen has tons of counter space, an island prep, and nearly new appliances. NEW Roof 2018. NEW AC 2019. NEW Water Softener 2020. NEW Drainfield 2022.
